modName: FXAA script - Odie s Vanilla Redux Shader v0_6
summary: FXAA script designed on demand. It\'s a simple sharpen filter and contrast increase that has little to no FPS drops.
descriptionHtml:
FXAA script designed on demand for me and a couple of streamers. It\'s a simple sharpen filter that has little to no FPS drops. Colours are slightly reworked to adress the green shades.

v0.6 Reintroduced Techinicolor and reworked the tonemap. The sky now looks less bloomed out.
As of now the screenshots are outdated. It hasn\'t deviated too much from the old versions, though.

FXAA injector mod required: [url]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=131[/url]
Based upon NO FPS DROP: [url]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=467[/url]
author: Odie Herpaderp
